heading: Forsaken Quarry Dungeon Guide
content: Forsaken Quarry offers early Rogue Flurry players a useful AoE  in . More importantly, it is a destination on your to unlock your Specialization! As a Rogue, you'll never miss this dungeon, so make sure to complete it on your way down! While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
